gov.nih.nci.ncia.grid.outgoing
Class NCIAQueryServiceBrokerImpl

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nci.ncia.grid.outgoing.NCIAQueryServiceBrokerImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
NCIAQueryServiceBrokerIF
public class NCIAQueryServiceBrokerImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements NCIAQueryServiceBrokerIF

This is the touch point for outgoing grid calls for the running NCIA node. Each remote manager must have an instance of this object to initiate requests and receive the results from the grid.
